# ARENA MASTER - DESIGN SYSTEM SPEC

## COLORS
- Primary (Gold): #B89E5D
- Background (Deep Blue): #1B303F
- Surface (Paper White): #F4F1E8
- Error (Red): #D9534F

## TYPOGRAPHY
- Headings: Montserrat Black (Uppercase)
- Subtitles/Buttons: Oswald Bold
- Body: Inter Regular

## COMPONENTS
- Primary Button: Background Gold, Text Deep Blue, Radius 8px.
- Cards: Background Paper White, Radius 12px, Seigaiha (Wave) Texture 5% opacity.
- Inputs: Background Deep Blue, Border 1px Gold, Text Paper White.

## ICONOGRAPHY
- Style: Line Art (2px stroke)
- Themes: Torii Gate, Cranes, Fists, Trophies.